S. Becker, K. Tabelow, S. Mohammadi, N. Weiskopf, J. Polzehl. Adaptive smoothing
of multi-shell diffusion-weighted magnetic resonance data by msPOAS.
Neuroimage, 2014, 95, 90-105. DOI:10.1016/j.neuroimage.2014.03.053.
}

